import personalHeadshot from '../../assets/images/headshot3.png';
import '../ProjectSection.css';

/* For the about me section on the front page */
export const aboutMe = {
    exactClassName: 'home__hero-section home__hero-section-alt aboutmeBg',
    rowClass: 'row home__hero-row hero-alt',
    flexDirection: 'row',
    textWrapper: 'home__hero-text-wrapper home__hero-text-wrapper-alt',
    topLineClass: 'top-line top-line-alt',
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    headlineClass: 'heading heading-alt',
    headline: 'Sarah Collins',
    descriptionClass: 'home__hero-subtitle home__hero-subtitle-alt dark',
    description:    
      "Hello! I am a recent Spring 2021 graduate from Embry-Riddle Aeronautical University with a Bachelor's of Science in \
       Software Engineering, seeking an entry-level role within the gaming industry.",
    displayButtonBool: true,
    imgStart: '',
    heroimg: true,
    img: personalHeadshot,
    alt: 'Personal Headshot'
  };
